_sText:
Very good Gun Game/Fight Yard map with textures of type "dev/". The map have a center field, a lateral higher ones and another one in the down side.
To play on it is simple:
1- Download the file
2- Open the .rar
3- Inside the .rar there is 6 Screenshots of the map and an archive .bsp and .nav
4- Put this 2 files (.bsp and .nav) in your map document.
eg: ...\Steam\SteamApps\<your-account>\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

Enjoy the Map and rate it plz <=)

The Evil
